A little throwback to when I used to own Salon VASO in #miamibeach.. 
I had the pleasure to do this beauties hair. 😊 @adrianalima 
#hairdressing #forte #luckyme 🖤

I get asked often.. what do I use on my hair. So here is my little cocktail. 
.
1. CLEAN shampoo. I leave it on for a minimum of 5 minutes. The yummy seaweed chunks in the shampoo gently exfoliate my hair and scalp allowing space for new growth.
~ 2. SMOOTH conditioner. I usually apply and rinse most of it but leave some in. Thickens and moisturizes my curly hair. 
~3. REPAIRED serum.  Applied everywhere from root to ends. Helps keep my hair from frizzing, my ends never split and protects from heat. 

It’s the greatest leave treatment 
for everyone. 

Working on a tutorial for my curly haired lovers out there. 😉

Enjoy 😉 

P.s. to my friends here in beautiful Cyprus.  I have a limited supply available for you here. 😊

The wind took over ☺️ 
Happy weekend lovers 🥂🍾
